                    <h1>Mobile</h1>
                    <h4>Mobile is everywhere!</h4>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item">
                <img src="img/bigdata.jpg" alt="big data" class="center-block" >
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Big Data</h1>
                    <h4>More and more data - how to manage it?</h4>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item">
                <img src="img/iot.jpg" alt="iot" class="center-block" >
